{"tid":244307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會開班 460蚊教文件轉檔","createTime":"2017-05-15T10:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T17:31:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50f6776b2478c593350609fa3f61abd3d39943e4","tid":244307,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170515/large/1494843679_7258.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170515%2Flarge%2F1494843679_7258.png&h=14d5675c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英透過周浩鼎修改立法會調查佢收取UGL公司5千萬嘅研究範疇，但鼎鼎竟然將檔案正版原裝交畀立法會，結果畀人睇晒修改者正係特首辦，成為政界笑抦。<br />\n<br />\n八方問過立法會資訊科技界議員莫乃光，佢話一般嚟講，如果唔想畀人知道點樣改過份文件，只要將文件由「doc檔」（Word檔）轉為「pdf檔」，就唔會畀人見到修改嘅痕跡，佢仲話坊間都有唔少機構有搞呢類點樣用Word嘅基本電腦課程㗎，例如工聯會。<br />\n<br />\n八方上過工聯會業餘進修中心網頁，發現真係有電腦課程叫做「Acrobat PDF電子文件製作」，教授學員「將doc檔轉成pdf檔」，下月16日就開班。成個課程460蚊，五個半鐘，一日搞掂，鼎鼎一個月嘅議員人工，足夠讀200次有多。工聯會立法會議員麥美娟被問到呢個課程時笑笑口話，工聯會嘅課程向來好受歡迎，歡迎在職人士多啲進修，為自己增值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56697181&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56697181%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=a6485667\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56697181%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170515&h=4622e69a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56697181&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170515</a>"},{"pid":"59a5a341becd4961f14e922ab8da1aeb0cc15aa3","tid":244307,"uid":28015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"另存新檔-&gt;.pdf<br />\n<br />\n承惠$460"},{"pid":"bda4ba5cacfd0c1dbb4b8689a5d6713e08